      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RITZA SOPHIE (3) could not have been more impressive last start in her a blistering 29.73 win at this track over 520m. Has the ability and expected to go close again. SPRING ROTA (2) is having his first look at this course. Comes here after a last start 4th and beaten 9 lengths (23.14) at Richmond. Hard to knock his form from this box, unbeaten in two starts. Great chance to atone. MY BABY BROOKE (4) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a nose second (29.73) in a Grade 5 at this track.",
